"https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-wrapped-most-streamed-k-pop-songs-artists-2023-newjeans-jungkook-3551714">但四重奏仍然是 Spotify 年度第二大流媒体韩国流行音乐表演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>率先报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yg-entertainment-share-price-shoot-up-after-blackpink-contract-renewal-3554195">BLACKPINK 续约后，YG Entertainment 股价飙升</a>。</p> ;
